file_content.text: The quantum bomb was not my best idea. I know, I know.
I did this to protect the Alliance, not destroy our fleet.
Almost done. Knew we could do this together.
My crew, Lana, you... I never meant to risk your lives.
I'm not losing my ship to Vaylin. Not today. Not ever.
I told you SCORPIO was bad news. Now look at us.
I just wanted to save people. Never thought it'd come to this.
Let's finish this, Commander--and save the Gravestone.
One down. Let's not think about how many are left.
A few more fuses. Let's keep moving.
We might just pull this off.
We're close. Just one more left.
